@startuml
actor "User" as User
participant "Web Frontend" as Frontend
participant "API Gateway\n(Kong)" as Kong
participant "Payment Service" as PaymentService
database "Payment DB" as DB

== Luồng nghiệp vụ: Tra cứu lịch sử giao dịch ==

User -> Frontend: Click xem "Lịch sử giao dịch"
activate Frontend

Frontend -> Kong: GET /code-payment-service/subscriptions/history\n?skip=0&limit=20\n[Authorization: Bearer <token>]
activate Kong
Kong -> PaymentService: Chuyển tiếp yêu cầu đã xác thực
activate PaymentService

PaymentService -> DB: findAllByUserId(userId, skip, limit)
activate DB
DB --> PaymentService: Danh sách Transaction
deactivate DB

PaymentService -> DB: countAllByUserId(userId)
activate DB
DB --> PaymentService: total
deactivate DB

PaymentService -> PaymentService: Map TransactionHistoryItem\n{id, plan_id, base_amount,\ndiscount_amount, final_amount,\npayment_status, payment_method,\npaid_at, created_at}
PaymentService --> Kong: BaseResponse\n{ data: { items, total } }
deactivate PaymentService
Kong --> Frontend: Trả về BaseResponse
deactivate Kong

Frontend -> Frontend: apiHelper bóc data\nHistoryList fallback final_amount/payment_status
Frontend --> User: Hiển thị bảng lịch sử giao dịch
deactivate Frontend

@enduml
